Package iaik.x509.extensions.priv

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IdentityLinkIssuer
    This class implements the IdentityLinkIssuer Extension as used in Austrian E-Government for certificates that are authorized to issue identity links.
    MandateIssuer
    This class implements the MandateIssuer Extension as used in Austrian E-Government for certificates that are authorized to issue electronic mandates.
    Officials
    This class implements the Officials extension as used for characterizing public authorities in Austrian E-Government.
    PublicAuthorityIdentifier
    This class implements the PublicAuthorityIdentifier extension as used for characterizing public authorities in Austrian E-Government.
    PublicServiceProvider
    This class implements the PublicServiceProvider Extension as used in Austria for institutions that provide some kind of public service.
